1557773.title: Brooklyn - Broadway - Grove Street (northwest corner)
1557773.folder: Brooklyn & Broadway & Grove Street (northwest corner), Brooklyn, NY

704723f-a.title: Brooklyn: Grove Street - Broadway
704723f-a.text:
(1)
Grove Strcet, east side, north of Broadway, showing property of
Loftus Wood at No. 16-18 (the house with the porch). This property
which was badly damaged by fire en September 22, 1924, does net appear
on the realty maps of 1929.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, another view. Loftus Wood was president of the Frank-
lin Ave. R.R. Ce., now the Franklin Ave. Trolley line.
January 4, 1923.
Eugene L. Arruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3)
The same, another view.
1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
